name: Problem Starting
meta_description: Need a new car battery? Roda provides car battery installation and a jump-start or a tow if your battery is dead. Multi-point inspection is included.

name: Oil Change - SUV
description:
A full-service Roda Oil Change includes a full change of your vehicle's motor oil with whatever type of oil your card needs - full synthetic, a blend, or conventional. Our technician will also replace your oil filter. 

For a full synthetic oil change, the price is $80 for a Sedan and $90 for an SUV.

name: Balance and Rotate Tires
description: Tire rotation and balance is an important part of auto maintenance, and will extend the life of your tires and improve overall safety of your car.
meta_description: Balance & tire rotation helps reduce tire wear & tear. Roda's mobile auto repair service picks up your car, performs service, and drops it off - no extra charge.

name: Diagnose Brake System Issue
description: Your brakes are the most crucial safety feature of your vehicle. If your car is not stopping as quickly as expected, or you’re experiencing unusual sounds like screeching, grinding, or squealing noises when you apply pressure to your brakes, book your brake system diagnosis as soon as possible.
meta_description: Worried about an issue with your brakes? Roda performs brake inspections, diagnosing and recommending necessary brake repairs. Learn more.

name: Diagnose Check Engine Light
description:
A Check Engine Light diagnosis is an investigation beyond a visual inspection and quick code read (those are free!) to identify the root cause of what is making your Check Engine Light come on. 

Once we read the code and inspect the vehicle, we may know the cause right away and a diagnosis isn't necessary. However, in many cases, a deeper diagnosis is required.
meta_description: Is your check engine light on or flashing? We diagnose check engine lights, run error codes, & recommend repairs. Free pick up and drop off service included!

name: Deluxe Hand Detail
description:
A thorough deep clean of both the interior and exterior of your vehicle, complete with clay bar/wax treatment on the exterior and tire shine. Not your routine detail, this service is ideal for special occasions where you need your car to look good-as-new inside and out. Services include:

  • Full interior vacuum (includes trunk) 
  • Dust/clean dash console (every crack and crevice)
  • Shampoo, steam clean, and deodorize carpets and floor mats
  • Clean and condition leather (if applicable)
  • Clean and dress doors and windows
  • Wash and hand dry exterior 
  • Degreasing exterior to remove bugs and debris
  • Clay bar to deep clean paint
  • Apply a hand coat of premium wax 
  • Clean wheels and tire shine
meta_description: If your car needs a thorough interior and exterior cleaning, Roda's deluxe auto detail is perfect. Free valet service from your home included with every detail.

name: AC/Heating Issue
description: AC not blowing cold air? Heat not blowing warm air? No matter your air conditioning or heating issue, we can diagnose and fix the problem. Sometimes it's as simple as a clogged filter, or maybe your AC just needs a recharge. Other times, it may be a more complex issue with your radiator or cooling fan. This service will get to the root of the issue and ensure your AC/heating works as you need it to.
meta_description: Car won't cool down or heat up? Roda diagnoses AC or heating issues and repairs it. Use our mobile auto repair at no extra charge. D.C. & Surrounding areas.

name: Tire Issue
description: Sometimes things just fall flat…but there’s usually a reason. Let us diagnose your tire issue, repair or replace your tires, ensure proper tread depth, or provide your tire alignment service (recommended every 12,000 miles.)
meta_description: Roda helps with tire repairs, whether it's a flat, rotation, or a new set of tires. Serving the D.C. area, we offer rescue for emergency pick-ups and flat tire repair.

description: Let's face it, it's probably been a while since you replaced these. For $40, we'll swap in brand new wiper blades to keep your windshield clear and keep you safe on the road.

name: Interior Detail
description:
Our thorough interior detail includes vacuuming and shampooing of upholstery, along with deep cleaning of vents, drains, and other nooks and crannies where dust and gunk can accumulate.

  • Deep clean of interior including windows 
  • Clean dashboard and hard to reach nooks and crannies
  • Full vacuum of interior

meta_description: When you car's interior needs some attention, a Roda interior detail will have it looking like new. Free valet service included with every interior detail.

name: Headlight Restoration
description: More than just washing your headlights, this restoration service clean headlight oxidation and coats lenses to protect them, making sure you have visibility especially in adverse conditions. Restoration also includes repair of superficial scratches.

name: Alignment
description: An alignment is integral to helping your tires perform well and last a long time. If your car is “pulling” to one side or maybe your steering wheel is off-center, it may be time for an alignment. We charge a flat-rate of $139 for alignments.
meta_description: Roda's tire alignment service helps your tires last longer. With our mobile auto repair, we pick up, perform the alignment, and drop off your car after a light wash.

name: Replace Cabin Filter
description: Your cabin filter helps maintain the quality of air in the interior of your vehicle, and is a last line of defense between you and air intake (pollen, diesel exhaust, fumes) from the outdoors. It should be replaced regularly as it becomes clogged.

name: Oil Change
description:
A full-service Roda Oil Change includes a full change of your vehicle's motor oil with whatever type of oil your card needs - full synthetic, a blend, or conventional. Our technician will also replace your oil filter. 

For a full synthetic oil change, the price is $80 for a Sedan and $90 for an SUV.
meta_description: Roda offers a hassle-free mobile oil change - we come to you, do the work, and return your vehicle. Premium service at your doorstep. Book now!

description: Repairing a tire after a small puncture, like what you might encounter from a nail or road hazard, has never been easier.
meta_description: If you have a tire leak, a tire plug can help get your car back on the road. Roda can plug your tire and get you moving again.

name: Rotate Tires
description: Rotating your tires involves repositioning them according to a specific pattern that's right for your vehicle. This maintenance needs to be done about as often as you have oil changes (or every 5,000-7,500 miles depending on your drivetrain) to ensure that the treads on your tires wear evenly, and that your ability to do regular tasks--like braking safely and maintaining traction on slick surfaces, are not compromised.
meta_description: Need to have your tires rotated? Extend your tires lifespan with regular tire rotation. Free multi-point inspection included with every service.

name: Manufacturer Recommended Maintenance
description: Maintenance Minder B? MAINTREQ? Is your car alerting you that's time for “recommended maintenance”? At regular mileage intervals, your vehicle manufacturer recommends a set of prescribed basic services to keep your car running smoothly. We do it all, no matter your make or model. And don't worry - we'll provide an estimate of cost for you to approve before we start any work!
meta_description: Time for factory scheduled maintenance? Trust Roda to keep your car running like new. Free multi-point inspection and valet service included!

name: Mount and Balance 1 Tire
description: Whenever you need to replace tires, or if there is more weight applied to a specific tire than another, mounting & balancing is necessary.
meta_description: Mounting and balancing new or replacement tires is easy with Roda. We pick-up, we repair, we drop off your car.

Replace Battery
description: Battery died? Replacement is easy through Roda.
meta_description: Battery replacement for your car, truck, or SUV is easy with Roda. We pick-up, we repair, we drop off.

name: Engine Bay Cleaning
description: A deep clean of your engine bay prevents vital components from damage and corrosion. Leaf litter or pine needles and other material can build-up over time, causing more expensive repairs over time. Keeping the intake for the climate control clear is important, and a valuable part of washing the engine bay.

name: Diagnose Fluid Leak
description: Puddle under your vehicle? A minor fluid leak can lead to major repairs if left undiagnosed. Roda can help you diagnose and fix a fluid leak before it turns into a big issue.

name: Replace Engine & Cabin Filters - Breathe Easy Pack
Coolant System Pressure Test
description: Pressure is vital for your coolant system because it ensures fluids maintain contact with the engine and cylinders, preventing your radiator from boiling over. If your car is running hot or there is a suspected coolant leak, this test may be recommended.
meta_description: AC issue? Need a coolant system pressure test? Roda has you covered. We pick up, perform the pressure test, and drop off your car after a light wash.

name: Replace Alternator
description: Your alternator is a generator that powers your engine, and recharges your battery. If it’s failing, you may notice that the car won’t start, your electrical display flickers, and there could be strange noises or the smell of burning wires from under the hood.
meta_description: Replacing the alternator on your car is easy with Roda. We pick-up, we service, and drop off your car.

name: Replace Blower Motor
description: Your blower motor moves air through the vents in your car. If you’re not feeling any air or heated air coming out of your vents, this could indicate an issue with your blower motor.

name: Replace Brake Caliper - Front
description: Brake calipers are a crucial component of your braking system, or being able to stop your car. When they become worn or damaged, they must be replaced. We can help you replace brake calipers, pads, or rotors conveniently and effectively.
meta_description: Quickly and easily get brake caliper replacement and repair with Roda. We pick-up, we repair, we drop off.

name: Replace Key Fob Battery
meta_description: Quickly and easily replace your key fob battery with Roda. We pick-up, we repair, we drop off. Call or book your key fob replacement service today.

name: Replace O2 Sensor(s)
description: An illuminated Check Engine Light might mean it’s time to replace your vehicle’s O2 sensors. The modern vehicle has many, many sensors responsible for regulating vital functions - the O2 sensor is one of the most important.

name: Replace Power Steering Rack & Pinion Assembly
Replace Spark Plugs
description: Spark plugs: the small but mighty part that makes your vehicle run. Roda can ensure your car stays safe on the road when it’s time to replace your spark plugs.

name: Replace Starter
description: Hear a click, but your engine hasn’t started? Instrument panel working, but can’t drive? The starter is a small gear that powers your engine on, and could be the root cause of these questions and more. Get in today for fast & easy repair of this component.
meta_description: Quickly and easily replace the starter in your car with Roda. We pick-up, we repair, we drop off. Call or book your starter replacement service today.

name: Replace Valve Cover Gasket
description: If you notice oil collecting in your engine bay or around your spark plugs, it could indicate a faulty valve cover, which puts your engine at risk of failure and significantly more expensive repairs.
meta_description: Quickly and easily replace the valve cover gasket on your car with Roda. We pick-up, we repair, we drop off.

name: Replace Wheel Bearings - Front
description: Wheel bearings ensure that your tires rotate smoothly. They are a vital component of your car, and sometimes repair insurance or a warranty will cover replacement–but if you’ve had your car for several years or a used car, this may be an out-of-pocket repair.
meta_description: Time to replace your wheel bearings? Roda has you covered. We pick up, inspect and replace the wheel bearings, and drop off your car after a light wash.

name: Brake Fluid Exchange
description: The hydraulic fluid that runs through your braking system is intended to minimize friction, and therefore it must withstand high heat. The majority of vehicles use Glycol-Ether based fluids that absorb moisture from the atmosphere, and can then cause corrosion, rust, and structural damage. For this reason, you need to have your brake fluid periodically flushed and replaced entirely with fresh fluid (called a brake fluid exchange.)
meta_description: Get your brakes checked or a brake fluid exchange with Roda and enjoy hassle-free car repair and maintenance, including complimentary pick-up and drop off of your vehicle.

name: Replace Sway Bar Links
description: Sway bar link replacement involves removing worn or damaged sway bar links and installing new ones to connect the sway bar to the suspension components, enhancing stability and reducing body roll during turns. This process improves handling and ride quality, ensuring safer and more comfortable driving conditions.
meta_description: Roda offers a hassle-free sway bar link replacement - we come to you, do the work, and return your vehicle. Premium service at your doorstep. Book now!

name: Replace Power Steering Pump
description: Your power steering pump is an important part of your steering system. It pressurizes the fluid that allows for safe and seamless steering - if your power steering pump fails, that means it won’t have the hydraulic support it needs to move the wheel fluidly. Control of the vehicle would require tremendous effort, and you may be unable to effectively steer/drive the vehicle.
meta_description: Trouble with your power steering? Diagnosing or replacing your power steering pump is easy with Roda. We pick-up, we repair, we drop off your vehicle.

name: Odor Removal
description: If there is an odor in your car that you just can’t get rid of, we can help with this special add-on service that can be combined with detailing. Our detailing team uses expert techniques and products (enzymatic cleaners, antimicrobial agents, etc.) to target and eliminate odors. This process can take some time, with several rounds of cleaning and ventilation using industrial fans to ensure your car comes back ready-to-drive.
meta_description: Strange odor in your vehicle? Roda can help! Just add on odor removal to any detail service. Free valet included with each service.

name: Replace Water Pump
description: While referred to as a “water pump,” this component actually circulates coolant fluid (usually mixed with antifreeze) through your engine and radiator. Rather than a pool of water under your car, if this pump is defective, you may see a puddle of synthetic fluid beneath the engine compartment.
meta_description: Quickly and efficiently replace your car's water pump with Roda. We pick-up. We repair. We drop off.

name: Serpentine Belt / Drive Belt Replacement
description: A drive belt, or “serpentine belt,” delivers power to your alternator, power steering, air conditioning, and possibly the water pump. This should be replaced when it becomes worn (before it breaks) to prevent your car from overheating, and to ensure your engine continues to receive power. Preventive maintenance that examines and replaces the belts when they become too worn helps avoid costly and inconvenient repairs.
